{"tid":1983030,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7.21中共策劃恐襲案9個月 黨衛軍於元朗區內截查多名年輕人","createTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:19:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"186d2ca60b893be474262804fa1a08342c54913c","tid":1983030,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"7.21事件9個月 防暴警於區內截查多名年輕人<br />\n21.04.2020 21:36<br />\n<br />\n今日是元朗7.21白衣人襲擊事件9個月，大批警員在元朗一帶巡邏戒備，有防暴警員要求街道上的人不要聚集。晚上近九點半，一批防暴警員在鳳翔路截查約十名年輕人，檢查他們的身份證及隨身物品。早前有數十人在連接港鐵元朗站的形點商場內中庭分散坐下，期間不時高叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282419&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282419%26csid%3D261_341&d=ltyh5TmdzGcNJFTF%2BAmR8t5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=8ddbe1f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282419&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a79858f14d7f250656f651b961b3b407f783332b","tid":1983030,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"收到風有患左武漢肺炎既手足<br />\n會特登行去俾黑警截查<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71964f5ea649c99d758a582a045c6d36a358e4dd","tid":1983030,"uid":120916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79858f14d7f250656f651b961b3b407f783332b","tid":1983030,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"收到風有患左武漢肺炎既手足<br />\n會特登行去俾黑警截查<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br